text: Dagana District is one of the 20 districts in Bhutan. The administrative centre is Daga. ==Administrative divisions== Dagana District is divided into fourteen village blocks: *Dorona Gewog *Drujegang Gewog *Gesarling Gewog *Goshi Gewog *Karmaling Gewog *Kana Gewog *Khebisa Gewog *Lajab Gewog *Lhamoy Zingkha Gewog *Nichula Gewog *Tashiding Gewog *Tsangkha Gewog *Tsendagang Gewog *Tseza Gewog Category:Districts of Bhutan
title: Dagana District
